text: Kalamullah Al-Hafiz bin Mat Rowi (born 30 July 1995) is a Malaysian footballer who plays for Malaysia Super League club Petaling Jaya City as a goalkeeper. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian footballers Category:Malaysia Premier League players Category:Malaysia Super League players Category:Felda United F.C. players Category:Petaling Jaya City FC players Category:Association football goalkeepers
